    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，Queued之后有哪些分支？是直接进入Running，还是有其他可能？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Queued",
        "Running"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Queued有三个出口：正常启动第一步进入Running，启动失败进入Failed，或者被用户取消进入Cancelled。另外用户也可以直接暂停，进入Paused。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Queued",
        "Running",
        "Failed",
        "Cancelled",
        "Paused",
        "Started First Step",
        "Problem starting First Step",
        "Cancelled by User"
